{
  "id": "adv_bond_suz_01_05",
  "title": "成宮すず5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "まったくお弁当を忘れて飛び出すなんて\nさくらはそそっかしいですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Goodness‚ running out and forgetting her lunchbox.\nSakura is truly such a scatterbrain.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 8.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "届けに来た私に感謝してほしいですわ\nあら、そろそろ約束の時間ですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She really should be grateful that I came to deliver it.\nOh‚ it's almost time for our meeting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃーん！　ありがとう！\nごめんね、お仕事の前に届けてくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chaaan! Thank you!\nSorry for making you come all this way before your work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.4333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 233.33333340000095
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふん、困ったものですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehehe‚ you're quite a handful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.1333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.1333329518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私が午後からお仕事で命拾いしましたわね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're lucky my work doesn't start until this afternoon!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.9333329518
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　だからお礼にコッソリ学校を案内するね！\nすずちゃんに見てほしいんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! So as a thank-you‚ I'll secretly show you around school!\nI really want you to see it‚ Suzu-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.9333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.3999996185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、私このままお仕事に向かわないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I really should be heading to work now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "午後からだよね？　まだ間に合うから大丈夫だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You said it's from the afternoon‚ right? You'll still make it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.6666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.6666662852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "遠慮しなくていいから！　ほら行っくよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't be modest! Come on‚ let's gooo!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolyard-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolyard-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.0999996185
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "ひぃー！　引っ張らないでくださいまし！\nほら、注目の的ですわ！　私お仕事がありますのー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hiee! Don't pull me like that!\nLook‚ everyone's watching! I have work to do!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0999996185,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1366.6670482
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.5833321889
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　ここが体育館です！　さっきまで授業で\nバスケットやってたんだよ。ダムダムダム",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ta-da! This is the gym! We were playing basketball\nhere in class just now. Dribble‚ dribble!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.6333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.2666659038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "普通ですわ！　体育館もバスケットも普通ですの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's ordinary! Both the gym and basketball are totally ordinary!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.2666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.2666655223
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "それでは、私そろそろおいとまさせて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now‚ if you'll excuse me‚ I'll be going…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.7999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.0666614533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "待って待って！　次は絶対すずちゃん好きだから！\n行かなきゃきっと後悔するよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ wait! I'm sure you'll love the next spot!\nYou'll definitely regret it if you don't go!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0666614533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_gym-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "gym-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9999947866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "もういいですわ！　私テレビ収録がありますの！\n引っ張らないでくださいましー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's enough! I have a TV recording!\nStop pulling meee!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9999947866,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_drag-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5119.2623553999965
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.68332812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "着っきました！　ここが図書室です！\nあらゆる本が読み放題だよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're here! This is the school library!\nYou can read all kinds of books as much as you want!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.73332812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.6999947866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "普通の図書館ですわ！　私の学校にもありますわ！\nいい加減もう行きますわよ！　ごきげんよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just a normal library! My school has one too!\nThat's quite enough‚ I'm leaving now! Good day!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.6999947866,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "待てーい！　待て待て待てーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold it right there! Wait‚ wait‚ wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.63332812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.63332812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "これで終わり、次で最後！　泣きの一回！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is really the end‚ the last one! Just one more time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3999992371,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_library-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "library-00-noon",
      "startTime": 124.5666614533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……もう本当に最後ですわよ\n何もなかったら、お仕事に向かいますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sigh… This really is the last one.\nIf there's nothing there‚ I'm heading straight to work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5666614533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.9166614533
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "なんの変哲もない廊下ですわ……少しでも信じた自分を\n呪いたいですわ。もう行きますわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just a plain old hallway… I want to curse\nmyself for believing you even for a bit. I'm leaving.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.9666614533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "違うよ、すずちゃん！　そっちの売店だよ\nここのね、とんかつサンドを食べてほしかったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ Suzu-chan! It's the shop over there!\nI really wanted you to try the tonkatsu sandwich here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5666614533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "早めに来ると買えちゃうから狙ってたんだ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was aiming for it since you can get it if you're early~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.33332812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolhallway-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolhallway-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.33332812
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_suz_01_05-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく美味しいんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's super‚ super delicious!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.9666659038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
